HEADWORD: Biting in
<hw>Bit"ing in"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <fld>(Etching.)</fld> <def>The
process of corroding or eating into metallic plates, by means of an
acid. See <er>Etch</er>.</def> <rj><au>G. Francis.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
